Description: Meta package for the Zig programming language (stable)
 This meta package depends on zig-stable and ensures the zig command
 is available via update-alternatives.

Package: zig-stable
Architecture: amd64 arm64 armel riscv64 ppc64el i386 loong64 s390x
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Zig programming language compiler (stable release)
 Zig is a general-purpose programming language and toolchain for maintaining
 robust, optimal, and reusable software.
 .
 This package provides the stable release of the Zig compiler and standard
 library, installed under /usr/lib/zig/{version}/ and made available as
 /usr/bin/zig via update-alternatives.
